# 金蝶云苍穹数据模型详解

## 1. 数据模型概述

### 1.1 数据模型设计原则
- **规范化**：遵循第三范式，避免数据冗余
- **可扩展**：预留扩展字段，支持自定义属性
- **一致性**：统一命名规范和数据类型
- **性能优化**：合理设计索引，提升查询性能

### 1.2 命名规范
- **表名**：小写+下划线，如`fin_voucher`
- **字段名**：小写+下划线，如`voucher_no`
- **主键**：统一使用`id`（BIGINT）
- **外键**：`{关联表}_id`，如`customer_id`
- **时间字段**：`create_time`, `update_time`
- **删除标记**：`is_deleted`（TINYINT）
- **状态字段**：`status`（VARCHAR）

### 1.3 数据类型规范

| 字段类型 | MySQL类型 | C#类型 | 说明 |
|---------|----------|--------|------|
| 主键ID | BIGINT | long | 自增主键 |
| 编码 | VARCHAR(50) | string | 业务编码 |
| 名称 | VARCHAR(200) | string | 业务名称 |
| 金额 | DECIMAL(18,2) | decimal | 金额字段 |
| 数量 | DECIMAL(18,4) | decimal | 数量字段 |
| 日期 | DATE | DateTime | 日期 |
| 时间 | DATETIME | DateTime | 日期时间 |
| 布尔 | TINYINT(1) | bool | 0/1 |
| 状态 | VARCHAR(20) | string | 状态枚举 |
| 备注 | TEXT | string | 长文本 |
| JSON | JSON | string | JSON数据 |

---

## 2. 财务云数据模型

### 2.1 凭证相关表

#### 2.1.1 凭证主表（fin_voucher）
```sql
CREATE TABLE fin_voucher (
  id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '主键ID',
  voucher_no VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '凭证号',
  voucher_date DATE NOT NULL COMMENT '凭证日期',
  voucher_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL COMMENT '凭证类型（记、转、收、付）',
  status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'draft' COMMENT '状态（draft草稿/audited已审核/posted已过账）',
  entry_count INT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '分录数',
  debit_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '借方金额',
  credit_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '贷方金额',
  create_time DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '创建时间',
  update_time DATETIME DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '更新时间',
  create_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '创建人',
  update_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '更新人',
  audit_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '审核人',
  audit_time DATETIME COMMENT '审核时间',
  post_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '过账人',
  post_time DATETIME COMMENT '过账时间',
  remark TEXT COMMENT '备注',
  is_deleted TINYINT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '删除标记（0正常/1删除）',
  UNIQUE KEY uk_voucher_no (voucher_no),
  KEY idx_voucher_date (voucher_date),
  KEY idx_status (status)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COMMENT='凭证主表';
```

**字段说明：**

| 字段名 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |
|-------|------|------|--------|------|
| id | BIGINT | 是 | 自增 | 主键ID |
| voucher_no | VARCHAR(50) | 是 | - | 凭证号，唯一 |
| voucher_date | DATE | 是 | - | 凭证日期 |
| voucher_type | VARCHAR(20) | 是 | - | 凭证类型：记、转、收、付 |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | 否 | draft | 状态：draft草稿/audited已审核/posted已过账 |
| entry_count | INT | 否 | 0 | 分录数 |
| debit_amount | DECIMAL(18,2) | 否 | 0 | 借方金额 |
| credit_amount | DECIMAL(18,2) | 否 | 0 | 贷方金额 |
| create_time | DATETIME | 是 | NOW() | 创建时间 |
| update_time | DATETIME | 否 | NULL | 更新时间 |
| create_by | VARCHAR(50) | 否 | NULL | 创建人 |
| update_by | VARCHAR(50) | 否 | NULL | 更新人 |
| audit_by | VARCHAR(50) | 否 | NULL | 审核人 |
| audit_time | DATETIME | 否 | NULL | 审核时间 |
| post_by | VARCHAR(50) | 否 | NULL | 过账人 |
| post_time | DATETIME | 否 | NULL | 过账时间 |
| remark | TEXT | 否 | NULL | 备注 |
| is_deleted | TINYINT | 否 | 0 | 删除标记 |

**C#实体类定义：**
```csharp
public class Voucher
{
    public long Id { get; set; }
    public string VoucherNo { get; set; }
    public DateTime VoucherDate { get; set; }
    public string VoucherType { get; set; }
    public string Status { get; set; } = "draft";
    public int EntryCount { get; set; }
    public decimal DebitAmount { get; set; }
    public decimal CreditAmount { get; set; }
    public DateTime CreateTime { get; set; }
    public DateTime? UpdateTime { get; set; }
    public string CreateBy { get; set; }
    public string UpdateBy { get; set; }
    public string AuditBy { get; set; }
    public DateTime? AuditTime { get; set; }
    public string PostBy { get; set; }
    public DateTime? PostTime { get; set; }
    public string Remark { get; set; }
    public bool IsDeleted { get; set; } = false;

    // 导航属性
    public List<VoucherEntry> Entries { get; set; }
}

public enum VoucherType
{
    记 = "记",
    转 = "转",
    收 = "收",
    付 = "付"
}

public enum VoucherStatus
{
    Draft = "draft",
    Audited = "audited",
    Posted = "posted"
}
```

#### 2.1.2 凭证分录表（fin_voucher_entry）
```sql
CREATE TABLE fin_voucher_entry (
  id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '主键ID',
  voucher_id BIGINT NOT NULL COMMENT '凭证ID',
  line_no INT NOT NULL COMMENT '行号',
  account_code VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '科目编码',
  account_name VARCHAR(200) COMMENT '科目名称',
  debit_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '借方金额',
  credit_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '贷方金额',
  summary VARCHAR(500) COMMENT '摘要',
  aux_account_1 VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '辅助核算1',
  aux_account_2 VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '辅助核算2',
  aux_account_3 VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '辅助核算3',
  create_time DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '创建时间',
  update_time DATETIME DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '更新时间',
  create_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '创建人',
  update_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '更新人',
  is_deleted TINYINT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '删除标记',
  KEY idx_voucher_id (voucher_id),
  KEY idx_account_code (account_code),
  CONSTRAINT fk_voucher_entry FOREIGN KEY (voucher_id) REFERENCES fin_voucher(id)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COMMENT='凭证分录表';
```

**C#实体类定义：**
```csharp
public class VoucherEntry
{
    public long Id { get; set; }
    public long VoucherId { get; set; }
    public int LineNo { get; set; }
    public string AccountCode { get; set; }
    public string AccountName { get; set; }
    public decimal DebitAmount { get; set; }
    public decimal CreditAmount { get; set; }
    public string Summary { get; set; }
    public string AuxAccount1 { get; set; }
    public string AuxAccount2 { get; set; }
    public string AuxAccount3 { get; set; }
    public DateTime CreateTime { get; set; }
    public DateTime? UpdateTime { get; set; }
    public string CreateBy { get; set; }
    public string UpdateBy { get; set; }
    public bool IsDeleted { get; set; } = false;

    // 导航属性
    public Voucher Voucher { get; set; }
}
```

#### 2.1.3 科目表（fin_account）
```sql
CREATE TABLE fin_account (
  id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '主键ID',
  account_code VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '科目编码',
  account_name VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL COMMENT '科目名称',
  account_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL COMMENT '科目类型（asset资产/liability负债/equity权益/revenue收入/expense费用）',
  direction VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL COMMENT '方向（debit借/credit贷）',
  level INT NOT NULL COMMENT '级次',
  parent_id BIGINT COMMENT '父科目ID',
  is_leaf TINYINT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '是否叶子节点（0否/1是）',
  is_controlled TINYINT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '是否受控科目（0否/1是）',
  cash_flow_item VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '现金流量项目',
  create_time DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '创建时间',
  update_time DATETIME DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '更新时间',
  is_deleted TINYINT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '删除标记',
  UNIQUE KEY uk_account_code (account_code),
  KEY idx_parent_id (parent_id),
  KEY idx_account_type (account_type)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COMMENT='科目表';
```

**C#实体类定义：**
```csharp
public class Account
{
    public long Id { get; set; }
    public string AccountCode { get; set; }
    public string AccountName { get; set; }
    public string AccountType { get; set; }
    public string Direction { get; set; }
    public int Level { get; set; }
    public long? ParentId { get; set; }
    public bool IsLeaf { get; set; } = false;
    public bool IsControlled { get; set; } = false;
    public string CashFlowItem { get; set; }
    public DateTime CreateTime { get; set; }
    public DateTime? UpdateTime { get; set; }
    public bool IsDeleted { get; set; } = false;

    // 导航属性
    public Account Parent { get; set; }
    public List<Account> Children { get; set; }
}

public enum AccountType
{
    Asset = "asset",
    Liability = "liability",
    Equity = "equity",
    Revenue = "revenue",
    Expense = "expense"
}

public enum AccountDirection
{
    Debit = "debit",
    Credit = "credit"
}
```

#### 2.1.4 科目余额表（fin_account_balance）
```sql
CREATE TABLE fin_account_balance (
  id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '主键ID',
  account_code VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '科目编码',
  account_name VARCHAR(200) COMMENT '科目名称',
  period VARCHAR(7) NOT NULL COMMENT '期间（YYYY-MM）',
  beginning_balance DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '期初余额',
  debit_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '本期借方发生额',
  credit_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '本期贷方发生额',
  ending_balance DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '期末余额',
  create_time DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '创建时间',
  update_time DATETIME DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '更新时间',
  UNIQUE KEY uk_account_period (account_code, period),
  KEY idx_period (period)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COMMENT='科目余额表';
```

**C#实体类定义：**
```csharp
public class AccountBalance
{
    public long Id { get; set; }
    public string AccountCode { get; set; }
    public string AccountName { get; set; }
    public string Period { get; set; } // 格式：YYYY-MM
    public decimal BeginningBalance { get; set; }
    public decimal DebitAmount { get; set; }
    public decimal CreditAmount { get; set; }
    public decimal EndingBalance { get; set; }
    public DateTime CreateTime { get; set; }
    public DateTime? UpdateTime { get; set; }
}
```

### 2.2 应收应付相关表

#### 2.2.1 应收单表（fin_ar_bill）
```sql
CREATE TABLE fin_ar_bill (
  id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '主键ID',
  bill_no VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '单据号',
  bill_date DATE NOT NULL COMMENT '单据日期',
  bill_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL COMMENT '单据类型（invoice发票/other其他）',
  customer_id BIGINT NOT NULL COMMENT '客户ID',
  customer_code VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '客户编码',
  customer_name VARCHAR(200) COMMENT '客户名称',
  amount DECIMAL(18,2) NOT NULL COMMENT '应收金额',
  paid_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '已收金额',
  unpaid_amount DECIMAL(18,2) DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '未收金额',
  status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'draft' COMMENT '状态（draft草稿/audited已审核/closed已结清）',
  create_time DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '创建时间',
  update_time DATETIME DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP COMMENT '更新时间',
  create_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '创建人',
  update_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '更新人',
  audit_by VARCHAR(50) COMMENT '审核人',
  audit_time DATETIME COMMENT '审核时间',
  remark TEXT COMMENT '备注',
  is_deleted TINYINT DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '删除标记',
  UNIQUE KEY uk_bill_no (bill_no),
  KEY idx_customer_id (customer_id),
  KEY idx_bill_date (bill_date),
  KEY idx_status (status)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COMMENT='应收单表';
```

**C#实体类定义：**
```csharp
public class ARBill
{
    public long Id { get; set; }
    public string BillNo { get; set; }
    public DateTime BillDate { get; set; }
    public string BillType { get; set; }
    public long CustomerId { get; set; }
    public string CustomerCode { get; set; }
    public string CustomerName { get; set; }
    public decimal Amount { get; set; }
    public decimal PaidAmount { get; set; } = 0;
    public decimal UnpaidAmount { get; set; } = 0;
    public string Status { get; set; } = "draft";
    public DateTime CreateTime { get; set; }
    public DateTime? UpdateTime { get; set; }
    public string CreateBy { get; set; }
    public string UpdateBy { get; set; }
    public string AuditBy { get; set; }
    public DateTime? AuditTime { get; set; }
    public string Remark { get; set; }
    public bool IsDeleted { get; set; } = false;
}

public enum ARBillType
{
    Invoice = "invoice",
    Other = "other"
}

public enum ARBillStatus
{
    Draft = "draft",
    Audited = "audited",
    Closed = "closed"
}
```

#### 2.2.2 收款单表（fin_receipt）
```sql
CREATE TABLE fin_receipt (
  id BIGINT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '主键ID',
  receipt_no VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL COMMENT '收款单号',
  receipt_date DATE NOT NULL COMMENT '收款日期',
  customer_id BIGINT NOT NULL COMMENT '客户ID',
